NK041(di)046:1: // gsang ba sngags kyi smon lam 'dod 'jo'i dga' ston bzhugs so //
NK041(di)046:2: dus gsum rgyal ba sras bcas ma lus dang //
NK041(di)046:3: 'gro ba'i skyabs gyur pad+ma sam b+ha wa //
NK041(di)046:4: srid zhi'i rgud pa kun sel rat+na'i zhabs //
NK041(di)046:5: mi 'bral snying nas gus pas phyag bagyi'o //
NK041(di)046:6: tshe 'di'i longs spyod rmi lam dga' ston bzhin //
NK041(di)046:7: lang tsho'i dpal yang 'ja' tshon lta bu ste //
NK041(di)046:8: tshe srog mi rtag glog gi zlos gar bzhin //
NK041(di)046:9: 'jig rten phun tshogs kun la dbang bsgyur kyang //
NK041(di)046:10: ston dus mdzes pa'i sprin dkar phung po bzhin //
NK041(di)046:11: skad cig mi rtag 'jig pa'i chos can du //
NK041(di)046:12: mthong nas srid par yid ni 'byung bar shog /
NK041(di)046:13: bde legs dngos grub kun gyi 'byung gnas ni /
NK041(di)046:14: mtshan nyid kun ldan theg mchog bshes gnyen te //
NK041(di)046:15: dran pa yis kyang srid zhi'i 'jigs 'phrog cing //
NK041(di)046:16: mi phyed dad pas tshul bzhin bsten par shog /
NK041(di)046:17: de ltar dge ba'i bshes las rnyed pa'i don //
NK041(di)046:18: gtan gyi skyabs gyur bla ma dkon mchog gsum //
NK041(di)046:19: yid la 'bral med gdung bas gsol 'debs shing //
NK041(di)046:20: 'gro kun pha mar shes pa'i snying rje yis //
NK041(di)046:21: kun gyi sdug bsngal rang gi len pa dang //
NK041(di)046:22: bdag gi bde dge ma lus gzhan la btang //
NK041(di)046:23: bla med bde la bdag gis 'god bya zhes //
NK041(di)046:24: sems ni byang chub dam pa bskyed byas pas //
NK041(di)046:25: phyin drug spyod pas nyin mtshan 'da' bar shog /
NK041(di)046:26: mngon mtho sgrub byed rgyal ba'i gsung rab kun //
NK041(di)046:27: don rnams skyes bu chung ngu'i lam dang ni //
NK041(di)046:28: thar pa bsgrub pa'i thabs la brtson pa yis //
NK041(di)046:29: chos kyi rnam grangs kun gyi brjod bya'i don //
NK041(di)046:30: skyes bu 'bring gi lam gyi rim pa ste //
NK041(di)046:31: nges par 'byung bas srid las grol bar shog /
NK041(di)046:32: rnam mkhyen go 'phang myur du bsgrub pa'i thabs //
NK041(di)046:33: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i theg chen rnam gnyis las //
NK041(di)046:34: ji bzhin gsungs pa'i gsang ba ma lus pa //
NK041(di)046:35: skyes bu chen po'i lam gyi rim pa ste //
NK041(di)046:36: bdag gis ma lus nye bar blangs pa las //
NK041(di)046:37: chos rnams thams cad rmi lam snang ba bzhin //
NK041(di)046:38: snang tsam de las yul gyi steng nyid du //
NK041(di)046:39: grub pa'i ngo bo rdul tsam ma mchis kyang //
NK041(di)046:40: las 'bras bslu ba med par nges rnyed nas //
NK041(di)046:41: bden gnyis zab mo'i gnad la goms par shog /
NK041(di)046:42: nyis brgya lnga bcu spong ba'i tshul khrims dang //
NK041(di)046:43: bcu bdun blang bya 'jug pa'i tshul khrims te //
NK041(di)046:44: kun gyi rtsa ba 'gram gzhi brtan po ni //
NK041(di)046:45: lhag pa'i tshul khrims 'dul sde la gnas shing //
NK041(di)046:46: bying rgod dri yi bzhon pas mi g.yo ba'i //
NK041(di)046:47: mngon rtogs rin chen rnam bzhi'i rang bzhin can //
NK041(di)046:48: ting 'dzin 'chi med ri bor gnas pa'i gzhi //
NK041(di)046:49: zab yangs mdo sde'i gnas la 'jog pa dang //
NK041(di)046:50: chos mngon gsal ba'i rnam dbye mig stong ldan //
NK041(di)046:51: gnas lugs rtogs pa'i ye shes lag nyal gyis //
NK041(di)046:52: mthar lta'i rmig pa 'dul byed lha yi dbang //
NK041(di)046:53: chos mngon blta na sdug pa'i grong khyer du //
NK041(di)046:54: sde snod gsum gyi rjod byed tshigs rnams dang //
NK041(di)046:55: brjod bya bslab pa rnam gsum mngon gyur shog /
NK041(di)046:56: de ltar rgyu yi theg pas rgyud sbyangs nas //
NK041(di)046:57: 'bras bu smin grol rdo rje theg pa'i lam //
NK041(di)046:58: nyams len drod rtags snang bzhi mngon gyur nas //
NK041(di)046:59: dam tshig dbang dbang shes rab rgyud 'chad cing //
NK041(di)046:60: man ngag lung sbyin nyams chag skong mdzad pa'i //
NK041(di)046:61: mthong thos dran reg slob dpon rnam bzhi las //
NK041(di)046:62: rgyud sde bzhi dang rdzogs pa chen po'i lam //
NK041(di)046:63: legs par bshad pa'i smin grol lam gyi gnad //
NK041(di)046:64: chu dbang sogs kyis rang rgyud smin byas nas //
NK041(di)046:65: mdun bskyed thugs kar yig 'bru'i sa bon bkod //
NK041(di)046:66: phyi yi spyod lam drang srong rjes mthun zhing //
NK041(di)046:67: nang gi nyi ma rnal 'byor snying la shar //
NK041(di)046:68: lha mo rnams dang phan tshun bltas pa las //
NK041(di)046:69: byung ba'i bde ba lam byed kri ya'i rgyud //
NK041(di)046:70: rje dpon lta bur dngos grub len pa dang //
NK041(di)046:71: rdo rje dril bu'i dbang gis smin byas nas //
NK041(di)046:72: bdag mdun gnyis ka'i thugs kar yig 'bru bkod //
NK041(di)046:73: phyi rol bya ba'i thabs dang nang ga ni //
NK041(di)046:74: zab mo'i rnal 'byor cha la mnyam par spyod //
NK041(di)046:75: 'dzum zhing dgod pa'i bde bas rnam rol pa //
NK041(di)046:76: yan lag bzhi la gzhol ba u pa'i rgyud //
NK041(di)046:77: grogs po lta bur dngos grub len par byed //
NK041(di)046:78: bya spyod gnas la tshul bzhin spyod par shog /
NK041(di)046:79: slob dpon dbang bskur rang rgyud smin byas nas //
NK041(di)046:80: bdag mdun gnyis ka dag pa'i lha ru bskyed //
NK041(di)046:81: ye shes spyan drangs de srid nga rgyal bzung //
NK041(di)046:82: phyag rgya bzhi yi rgya las mi 'da' zhing //
NK041(di)046:83: ting 'dzin gsum gyi lang tsho'i snying la 'grogs //
NK041(di)046:84: lag pa'i pad+mo 'brel ba'i bde bas mtshis //
NK041(di)046:85: nang gi rnal 'byor gtso bor gyur pa yi //
NK041(di)046:86: yi ge'i lam gyi gzhi la rnam grol shog /
NK041(di)046:87: rgyu dbang bskur nas rags pa'i phung sogs rnams //
NK041(di)046:88: phyi nang snod bcud gzhal yas lha rnams su //
NK041(di)046:89: dag pa'i sku dang mchog dbang gsum bskur nas //
NK041(di)046:90: bskyed rim tshogs zhing bsrung 'khor sngon 'gro bas //
NK041(di)046:91: rim pa lnga dang rjes mthun lam gyi 'gros //
NK041(di)046:92: khams drug ldan pa'i mi rnams phung khams sogs //
NK041(di)046:93: rim gyis thim nas 'chi ba'i rim pa'am //
NK041(di)046:94: ji ltar mtshan mo gnyid du song ba'i tshe //
NK041(di)046:95: yul lnga'i shes pa rim gyis yid du thim //
NK041(di)046:96: de yang kun gzhir thim pas mi rtog pa //
NK041(di)046:97: rtse gcig snang yul med pa'i ngang de nyid //
NK041(di)046:98: chos dbyings thim pas rang bzhin spros dang bral //
NK041(di)046:99: thun bar lhag mos 'od gsal du 'jug pa'i //
NK041(di)046:100: bar 'dir chos sku'i rnal 'byor la gnas shing //
NK041(di)046:101: gnyid dam 'chi bas 'od gsal lugs ldog tu //
NK041(di)046:102: slar yang mched pa'i kun gzhi'i rnam shes las //
NK041(di)046:103: yid gnyid gcig pu langs pas rmi lam sems //
NK041(di)046:104: dbang po kun tshangs yid kyi lus grub pa //
NK041(di)046:105: de mtshungs skad cig mngon byang lnga las ni //
NK041(di)046:106: dang po'i mgon po legs par bskyed pa'i tshul //
NK041(di)046:107: bar do sgyu lus longs skur ldang bar shog /
NK041(di)046:108: slar yang sad pa'i gnas skabs nyin snang du //
NK041(di)046:109: gdan gsum lha yi sku ru nges byas nas //
NK041(di)046:110: bar do'i lus de ma yi mngal du ni //
NK041(di)046:111: zhugs tshul dang po'i mgon po mi bskyod pa'i //
NK041(di)046:112: sku las zhugs pas rdo rje'i sems bskyed cing //
NK041(di)046:113: de la lus dkyil bkod cing sgo gsum dag /
NK041(di)046:114: byin gyis brlab cing sems dpa' gsum brtsegs su //
NK041(di)046:115: byas nas rigs ma'i 'dod yon rnal rol bas //
NK041(di)046:116: nyin snang skye shi'i bar do'i goms 'dris kyis //
NK041(di)046:117: skye ba sprul sku'i rnal 'byor lam byed shog /
NK041(di)046:118: de ltar rim pa dang po mthar phyin nas //
NK041(di)046:119: gsang ba'i sna rtser a ba d+hu ta'i nang //
NK041(di)046:120: dwangs ma'i thig le rang sems dbyer med du //
NK041(di)046:121: bzung bas mnyam bzhag dga' bzhi'i ting 'dzin dang //
NK041(di)046:122: rjes thob rigs brgya rigs lnga rigs gsum sogs //
NK041(di)046:123: bde stong dbyer med lha yi rnam rol bsgom //
NK041(di)046:124: slar yang dben pa gsum gyi rim pa dang //
NK041(di)046:125: kun rdzob sgyu ma don dam 'od gsal nyid //
NK041(di)046:126: bden gnyis dbyer med zung 'jug nyams len rnams //
NK041(di)046:127: gsang ba snying po dpal ldan 'dus pa dang //
NK041(di)046:128: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga ji bzhin du //
NK041(di)046:129: bskyed rdzogs zab mo'i don rnams mngon gyur shog /
NK041(di)046:130: mtshan nyid kun ldan bla ma yab yum las //
NK041(di)046:131: lam dbang zab mo'i legs par smin byas nas //
NK041(di)046:132: rnam dag dbang lnga'i chu bos sgrib gnyis kyi //
NK041(di)046:133: dri ma kun bkrus sku bzhi'i sa bon bzhag /
NK041(di)046:134: dam tshig sdom pa tshul bzhin bsrungs ba las //
NK041(di)046:135: zab mo'i lam bzang skye ba'i snod gyur pas //
NK041(di)046:136: ma dag skye shi bar do'i snang zhen rnams //
NK041(di)046:137: yid ngor sbyangs nas sku gsum lam khyer ba //
NK041(di)046:138: sbyang bzhi sbyang byed tshang ba'i bskyed rim gyis //
NK041(di)046:139: rim pa dang po'i lam la mngon gyur shog /
NK041(di)046:140: phyi nang rang lus dkyil 'khor lha yi tshogs //
NK041(di)046:141: rtsa yig bdud rtsi dpa' bo rnal 'byor ma //
NK041(di)046:142: thim lugs bzhi bsgom ye shes bskyed byed cing //
NK041(di)046:143: rdzogs rim rtogs pa 'dren pa'i rgyud smin byas //
NK041(di)046:144: nyi zla'i lam nas dkyil 'khor bcu yi rlung //
NK041(di)046:145: sgra gcan lam du 'gog pa'i thabs mkhas kyis //
NK041(di)046:146: mun pa'i lam nas 'bar ba'i tsan+da lis //
NK041(di)046:147: ham yig ri bong 'dzin pa zhu ba las //
NK041(di)046:148: lhan skyes bde bas mnyam bzhag drangs pa yis //
NK041(di)046:149: 'khor 'das chos rnams kun gyi gnas lugs dang //
NK041(di)046:150: dbyer med gyur pa dpe yi ye shes nyid //
NK041(di)046:151: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i sku ru langs pa las //
NK041(di)046:152: ma dag skye sha'i 'phrang las grol ba yi //
NK041(di)046:153: rdzogs rim a nu'i lam du 'jug par shog /
NK041(di)046:154: don gyi lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes ni //
NK041(di)046:155: a ti ye dag ro mnyam chen po nyid //
NK041(di)046:156: yod min med min stong min mi stong min //
NK041(di)046:157: rang bzhin gshis la gzhal na thams cad min //
NK041(di)046:158: med pa ma yin gnyis med zung 'jug ste //
NK041(di)046:159: rtag min chad min smra bsam brjod las 'das //
NK041(di)046:160: ngang gnas ye nas rdzogs pa chen po ni //
NK041(di)046:161: kun min phyogs tsam gzhal na thams cad min //
NK041(di)046:162: blo yis bkod na dran bsam brjod las 'das //
NK041(di)046:163: rnal ma'i don la kun ming brtags pa tsam //
NK041(di)046:164: ji ltar snang ba de yang wa le ba //
NK041(di)046:165: tshig gis ma bskyed lha sngags lhun gyis grub //
NK041(di)046:166: gang ltar bsam brjod 'das pa'i rang bzhin te //
NK041(di)046:167: a ti'i dgongs don tshul bzhin rtogs par shog /
NK041(di)046:168: khyad par 'od gsal rdo rje snying po'i don //
NK041(di)046:169: rang bzhin bab yin stong pas phan ci yod //
NK041(di)046:170: so ma ngang bzhag ma bcos rang ga ma //
NK041(di)046:171: tha mal shes pa rang grol rgyal ba'i lam //
NK041(di)046:172: rang gis rang grol gnyen pos bcos mi dgos //
NK041(di)046:173: ye grol bskyar bzhi med de gdod ma'i ngang //
NK041(di)046:174: cer grol ngo bo med de bden pas stong //
NK041(di)046:175: rang grol gnyen po med de rang bzhag nyid //
NK041(di)046:176: 'gyu grol rang sar dag ste skad cig ma //
NK041(di)046:177: shar grol dus mnyam yin te snga phyi med //
NK041(di)046:178: ma bcos rang bzhag rang babs ka dag klong //
NK041(di)046:179: ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje'i don rtog shog /
NK041(di)046:180: shes rab rang byung sgron ma'i dbyings rum nas //
NK041(di)046:181: rgyang zhags sgron mas rig gdangs sgo phye nas //
NK041(di)046:182: dag dbyings sgron mas sna tshogs rgyan bkram ste //
NK041(di)046:183: thig le stong sgron zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs //
NK041(di)046:184: dang po rgyu yis ma bskyed dbyings lnga shar //
NK041(di)046:185: bar du rkyen gyis ma bskyed tshom bur grub //
NK041(di)046:186: tha ma lta ba'i gnas dag dbyings rig 'dres //
NK041(di)046:187: yid dpyod dang bral mngon sum mthar phyin shog /
NK041(di)046:188: khreg chod lta bas srid khung gdar sha bcad //
NK041(di)046:189: thod rgal bsgoms pas sku gsum rtsal rdzogs te //
NK041(di)046:190: gdod nas rnam dag dang po'i sangs rgyas nyid //
NK041(di)046:191: dbyer med thig le'i gzugs su rang snang ba //
NK041(di)046:192: de las spros tshe sku gsum snod bcud dang //
NK041(di)046:193: bsdus tshe stong nyid snying rje chos kyi sku //
NK041(di)046:194: thig le nyag gcig yid la g.yo med shog /
NK041(di)046:195: slar yang rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK041(di)046:196: gnyis snang 'khrul ba'i bag chags kun bcom nas //
NK041(di)046:197: rim pa bzhi pa'i don gyi 'od gsal dang //
NK041(di)046:198: dbyer med lhan cig skyes pa bde ba'i dngos //
NK041(di)046:199: bden gnyis zung du 'jug pa'i he ru ka /
NK041(di)046:200: mkha' dbyings shar ba'i dbang po'i gzhu bzhin du //
NK041(di)046:201: gsal mdangs 'od zer lnga yi d+r+wa ba can //
NK041(di)046:202: stobs bcu mi 'jig bzhi dang so so rig /
NK041(di)046:203: ma 'dres bco brgyad rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang //
NK041(di)046:204: bla med yon tan rang bzhin gzhal med las //
NK041(di)046:205: rnam kun mchog ldan ngo bo chos kyi sku //
NK041(di)046:206: rnam pa longs spyod rdzogs sku grangs med kyis //
NK041(di)046:207: sprul pa'i sprin 'phro sku gsum dbyer med chog /
NK041(di)046:208: mkha' khyab gzugs bzung bgrang yas sems can la //
NK041(di)046:209: ji snyed khams dang bsam pa'i dbye ba bzhin //
NK041(di)046:210: rang rang skad du rgyu dang 'bras bu yi //
NK041(di)046:211: theg pa gnyis las brtsams pa'i chos kyi tshul //
NK041(di)046:212: legs par ston la skyo ngal med par shog /
NK041(di)046:213: 'di dang bar dor mchog gi go 'phang ni //
NK041(di)046:214: nges par grub pa'i lam bzang ma rnyed na //
NK041(di)046:215: zab lam 'pho ba'i rnal 'byor la goms pas //
NK041(di)046:216: rnam shes mkha' spyod gnas su 'pho byas te //
NK041(di)046:217: bskyed rdzogs lam gyi rim pa'i 'phro mthud shog /
NK041(di)046:218: de ltar rgyu lam 'bras bu khyad par las //
NK041(di)046:219: sku dang zhing khams 'khor dang mdzad pa ni //
NK041(di)046:220: yongs su dag pa'i ye shes lam nyid du //
NK041(di)046:221: byed dang mi byed sngags dang pha rol phyin //
NK041(di)046:222: so sor 'byed pa'i blo gros dang ldan shog /
NK041(di)046:223: bdag kyang 'di nas tshe rabs thams cad du //
NK041(di)046:224: rje btsun bla ma mchog dang mi 'bral zhing //
NK041(di)046:225: des gsungs gsung gi bdud rtsi myong ba dang //
NK041(di)046:226: de don sgrub la zhum pa med pa yis //
NK041(di)046:227: tshe rabs kun tu yongs 'dzin dam pa dang //
NK041(di)046:228: nam yang 'bral med rjes su 'dzin gyur cig /
NK041(di)046:229: ces pa'i gsang ba sngags kyi smon lam 'dod 'jo'i dga' ston zhes bya ba 'di yang /
NK041(di)046:230: dag pa'i snang ba lhur len pa rat+na'i mtshan dang /
NK041(di)046:231: skyes stobs kyi blo gros dang ldan pa'i chos rje rnam snang /
NK041(di)046:232: las dang smon lam gyis 'brel ba sras mo yum sras sogs kyis gsung gis bskul ngor /
NK041(di)046:233: pra dz+ny+aa rasmisa thub bstan rdo rje brag tu sbyar ba'o //
